  "prompt": "Where can I get best amenity room maintenance service in Sydney?",
  "response": "Finding the best amenity room maintenance service in Sydney depends on your specific needs, such as the type of amenities, location, and budget. Here are some highly regarded options to consider:\n\n### 1. **Professional Cleaning Companies**\n   - **Jim\u2019s Cleaning Sydney**: Known for reliable and thorough cleaning services, including amenity rooms. They offer tailored solutions and are highly rated by customers.\n   - **Absolute Domestics**: Specializes in commercial and residential cleaning, including amenity spaces. They have experienced cleaners and flexible scheduling.\n   - **Meter Maid**: Offers premium cleaning services for gyms, pools, and amenity rooms. They use eco-friendly products and advanced equipment.\n\n### 2. **Specialized Maintenance Providers**\n   - **Sydney Maintenance Services**: Focuses on maintaining and repairing amenity rooms, including pools, gyms, and common areas. They provide comprehensive care and regular maintenance plans.\n   - **All Needs Property Maintenance**: Offers a wide range of maintenance services, from cleaning to repairs, tailored for amenities in residential and commercial buildings.\n\n### 3. **Strata Management Companies**\n   - If you\u2019re part of a strata building, check with your strata management company. Many, like **Stratacare** or **Jamesons Strata Management**, have preferred contractors for amenity room maintenance.\n\n### 4. **Local Recommendations**\n   - Ask for referrals from neighbors, building managers, or local community groups. Word-of-mouth recommendations can lead you to trusted local providers.\n\n### 5. **Online Platforms**\n   - Use platforms like **Airtasker**, **Service.com.au**, or **HiPages** to find vetted professionals who specialize in amenity room maintenance.\n\n### Tips for Choosing the Right Service:\n   - **Check Reviews**: Look for companies with positive feedback and high ratings.\n   - **Request Quotes**: Compare prices and services to find the best fit.\n   - **Verify Experience**: Ensure the provider has experience with the type of amenities you need maintained.\n   - **Eco-Friendly Options**: If sustainability is important, ask about their use of environmentally friendly products.\n\nBy researching and comparing options, you can find the best amenity room maintenance service in Sydney that meets your requirements.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
